The footage, shot by Bronwyn Davids, shows the alleged killer, Mortimer Saunders, who was charged with Courtney's murder, standing in support of the family. It's believed he often joined the search for Courtney, and supported her parents. Saunders rented a room from the family and would often invite Courtney to watch cartoons in his room. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
